	<annotations>
		<text id="0" type="text/plain" rect="(335.0, -89.0, 150.0, 222.0)" font-family="Segoe UI" font-size="12">Make a data subset

1. by selecting rows where  udc_label_en is XX (of your choice)

2. by selecting rows where langauge_code is lav

3. by selecting rows where author is not an empty string (just leave the field empty).
</text>
		<text id="1" type="text/plain" rect="(508.0, -75.0, 85.0, 87.0)" font-family="Segoe UI" font-size="12">Add title and sub_title to used text features</text>
